    <item>
      <title>NPM</title>
      <link>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/npm/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Apr 2017 18:36:24 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/npm/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;alert &#xA;alert-warning&#34;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;role=&amp;ldquo;alert&amp;rdquo;&amp;gt;the CLI requires node version 8.0.0 or higher&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Codefresh&amp;rsquo;s CLI is available for installation through NPM registry.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Install:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;npm install -g codefresh&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Install a specific version:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;npm install -g codefresh@{VERSION}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Update to latest version:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;npm install -g codefresh&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Update to a specific version:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;npm install -g codefresh@${VERSION}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>YARN</title>
      <link>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/yarn/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Apr 2017 18:36:24 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/yarn/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;alert &#xA;alert-warning&#34;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;role=&amp;ldquo;alert&amp;rdquo;&amp;gt;the CLI requires node version 8.0.0 or higher&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Codefresh&amp;rsquo;s CLI is available for installation using YARN.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Install:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;yarn global add codefresh&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Install a specific version:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;yarn global add codefresh@{VERSION}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Update to latest version:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;yarn global upgrade codefresh&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Update to a specific version:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;yarn global upgrade codefresh@{VERSION}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Docker Image</title>
      <link>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/docker/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Apr 2017 18:36:24 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/docker/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;You can run the CLI using our official docker image which is published to &lt;a href=&#34;https://hub.docker.com/r/codefresh/cli/&#34;&gt;Dockerhub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Pull the latest version:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;docker pull codefresh/cli&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Pull a specific version:&#xA;&lt;code&gt;docker pull codefresh/cli:${VERSION}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Download</title>
      <link>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/download/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Apr 2017 18:36:24 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/download/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Navigate to &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/codefresh-io/cli/releases&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Official Releases&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;and download the binary that matches your operating system.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;We currently support the following OS: &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;https://github.com/codefresh-io/cli/releases/download/v1.1.4/codefresh-v1.1.4-alpine-x64.tar.gz&#39; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Alpine-x64&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;https://github.com/codefresh-io/cli/releases/download/v1.1.4/codefresh-v1.1.4-linux-x64.tar.gz&#39; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Linux-x64&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;https://github.com/codefresh-io/cli/releases/download/v1.1.4/codefresh-v1.1.4-macos-x64.tar.gz&#39; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Macos-x64&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;https://github.com/codefresh-io/cli/releases/download/v1.1.4/codefresh-v1.1.4-win-x64.zip&#39; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Windows-x64&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;https://github.com/codefresh-io/cli/releases/download/v1.1.4/codefresh-v1.1.4-alpine-arm64.tar.gz&#39; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Alpine-arm64&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#39;https://github.com/codefresh-io/cli/releases/download/v1.1.4/codefresh-v1.1.4-linux-arm64.tar.gz&#39; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Linux-arm64&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;After downloading the binary, untar or unzip it and your are good to go.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;You can also add the binary to your system PATH environment variable so you can use it easily.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If your operating system is missing please feel free to open us an issue in our &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/codefresh-io/cli/issues&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Github repository&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>HOMEBREW</title>
      <link>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/homebrew/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2018 12:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://codefresh-io.github.io/cli/installation/homebrew/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Install Codefresh CLI on macOS with &lt;a href=&#34;https://brew.sh&#34;&gt;Homebrew&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;install&#34;&gt;Install&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# tap Codefresh homebrew repo&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew tap codefresh-io/cli&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# install Codefresh CLI&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew install codefresh&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;update-to-the-latest-version&#34;&gt;Update to the latest version&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew upgrade codefresh&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;uninstall&#34;&gt;Uninstall&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#272822;background-color:#fafafa;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew uninstall codefresh&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
